ATTRIBUTION

This project is a fork of HianimeDownloader by G Heatherington:
https://github.com/gheatherington/HianimeDownloader

The original project has been significantly modified and extended with:
- Docker and Unraid support
- Modern web interface with dark theme
- Real-time progress tracking via Server-Sent Events
- Enhanced security features
- Comprehensive documentation

